election by the Bermuda Olympic Association under the universality policy, which aims to increase the diversity of participating nations.\n\nThe qualification period for swimming closes on June 23.\n\nHarvey’s brother, Jack, is in a similar position, having met the standard in the 100 backstroke at the AP Race London International.\n\n\n\n#StephenWrightReports#Swimming\n\nCategory:All,Sports\n\n.\n\nArchives:\n\nCategories:\n\nTags:\n\nBernews", "title": "Emma Harvey Hits Qualifying Standard - Bernews", "top-image": "https://adserver.bernews.com/openx/www/delivery/avw.php?zoneid=12&n=250e68e", "domain": "bernews.com", "lang": null, "author": "", "description": "", "keywords": ""}